===================================================================================

ðŸ“š WHAT IS THIS FILE?
---------------------
This is the MAIN LAYOUT TEMPLATE using EJS-Mate (layout engine).
All other pages extend this template using: <% layout("layouts/boilerplate") -%>

ðŸ”— HOW EJS-MATE WORKS:
---------------------
1. Child page sets: <% layout("layouts/boilerplate") -%>
2. Child page content goes into <%- body -%>
3. This template wraps around the child content

ðŸ“Œ TEMPLATE STRUCTURE:
---------------------
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    - Meta tags
    - CSS (Bootstrap, Font Awesome, Google Fonts, Custom)
  </head>
  <body>
    - Navbar (included from ../includes/navbar.ejs)
    - Container with <%- body -%> (child page content goes here!)
    - Footer (included from ../includes/footer.ejs)
    - JavaScript (Bootstrap JS, Custom script.js)
  </body>
</html>

ðŸ“– INTERVIEW TIP:
----------------
"I used EJS-Mate for template inheritance, which follows the DRY principle.
The boilerplate contains common elements like navbar and footer, while
individual pages only define their unique content."

===================================================================================
%>
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Smart Stay</title>
    
    <%# ===================== CSS STYLESHEETS ===================== %>
    
    <%# Custom CSS - Our own styles (loaded first so Bootstrap can be overridden) %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    
    <%# Bootstrap CSS - UI framework for responsive design %>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-sRIl4kxILFvY47J16cr9ZwB07vP4J8+LH7qKQnuqkuIAvNWLzeN8tE5YBujZqJLB" crossorigin="anonymous">
    
    <%# Font Awesome - Icon library %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/7.0.1/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-2SwdPD6INVrV/lHTZbO2nodKhrnDdJK9/kg2XD1r9uGqPo1cUbujc+IYdlYdEErWNu69gVcYgdxlmVmzTWnetw==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
    
    <%# Google Fonts - Plus Jakarta Sans (modern, clean font) %>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:ital,wght@0,200..800;1,200..800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <%# ===================== NAVBAR ===================== %>
    <%- include("../includes/navbar.ejs") %>
    
    <%# ===================== MAIN CONTENT ===================== %>
    <%# 
        <%- body -%> is where child page content is injected
        .container gives Bootstrap's responsive width + padding + centering
    %>
    <div class="container"><%- body -%></div>
    
    <%# ===================== FOOTER ===================== %>
    <%- include("../includes/footer.ejs") %> 
    
    <%# ===================== JAVASCRIPT ===================== %>
    
    <%# Bootstrap JS Bundle - Includes Popper.js for dropdowns, tooltips, etc %>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-FKyoEForCGlyvwx9Hj09JcYn3nv7wiPVlz7YYwJrWVcXK/BmnVDxM+D2scQbITxI" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    
    <%# Custom JavaScript - Form validation and other client-side logic %>
    <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>

